  "prompt": "Where is good apartment near Deloitte Chicago?",
  "response": "When looking for an apartment near Deloitte's Chicago office, which is located in the Deloitte Plaza at 111 South Wacker Drive, you will want to consider several neighborhoods that offer convenient access to public transportation and amenities. Here are some recommended neighborhoods and areas to look for apartments:\n\n1. **Loop**: This is the immediate area downtown where Deloitte is located. It's a bustling area with lots of amenities, restaurants, and easy access to public transportation.\n\n2. **River North**: Just north of the Loop, River North is known for its vibrant nightlife, art galleries, and dining. It\u2019s within walking distance to Deloitte.\n\n3. **West Loop**: A bit further west, this neighborhood has been rapidly developing and offers a trendy atmosphere with many dining and entertainment options.\n\n4. **South Loop**: This area provides easy access to the lakefront and has a mix of residential options. It\u2019s also within a reasonable commuting distance to the Loop.\n\n5. **Streeterville**: Located north of the Loop and adjacent to the lake, this area also offers a variety of housing options and is a bit more residential.\n\n6. **Gold Coast**: A bit more upscale, this neighborhood has many luxury apartments and is further north of the Loop, providing stunning views of the lake.\n\n### Tips for Finding an Apartment:\n- **Use Rental Websites**: Platforms like Zillow, Apartments.com, and Rent.com can provide listings based on your budget and desired amenities.\n- **Consider Public Transit**: Look for places near CTA train stations or bus routes if you plan on commuting.\n- **Visit Apartment Complexes**: Many complexes in these areas may offer tours or special promotions.\n- **Check Reviews**: Sites like Yelp or Google Reviews can give you insights into the management and quality of apartments.\n\nTry to consider your lifestyle preferences, commute, and budget when choosing the best fit for your needs. Good luck with your search!",
